Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.23,0:02:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,All the pirates who are after the One Piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.71,0:02:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,...head for the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.13,0:02:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,the second half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.02,0:02:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,However, no one has ever fully explored it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.32,0:02:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,except for Gold Roger, the Pirate King.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.38,0:02:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The New World has ruined many pirates' dreams and ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.40,0:03:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Monkey D. Luffy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.02,0:03:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,a boy whose body turned to rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.37,0:03:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and his friends venture into that sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.32,0:03:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna become the Pirate King!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.04,0:03:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,After surviving a fierce battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.08,0:03:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,the Straw Hats finally entered the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.35,0:03:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,the harshest sea ruled by the Four Emperors.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.28,0:03:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,After receiving an emergency signal, they landed on Punk Hazard Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.12,0:03:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a strange island divided into two parts;
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.34,0:03:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,the Burning Lands and the Ice Lands.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.60,0:03:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether it's the Straw Hats or Smoker,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.22,0:03:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,we can get rid of all those troublemakers
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.49,0:03:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,who are learning what's going on on this island at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.15,0:03:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Call Joker.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.90,0:03:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.16,0:03:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I never understood why you joined the Warlords in the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.73,0:03:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.27,0:04:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,There are things that you can't see
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.07,0:04:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,unless you change your standing, Smoker!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.02,0:04:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Scalpel!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.71,0:04:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,My heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.72,0:04:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have to tell you anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.10,0:04:56.11,B1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(2000,2000)}"Meeting Again After Two Years! Luffy and Law!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.46,0:05:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.64,0:05:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Tashigi-chan! He's way too strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.14,0:05:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.43,0:05:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't join the Navy to cower behind rocks!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.64,0:05:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You will get chopped up again in that film!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.82,0:05:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it up to Smo-yan for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.78,0:05:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? The film is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.57,0:05:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Now is our chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.49,0:05:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Alliga-taur!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.55,0:05:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.24,0:05:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,A ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.87,0:06:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it a warship?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.39,0:06:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So the Navy's here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.18,0:06:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What? I didn't see anything around here little while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.14,0:06:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on? Is the Master okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.09,0:06:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, somebody is there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.38,0:06:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.89,0:06:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.52,0:06:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's you! Do you remember me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.74,0:06:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your help the other day!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.43,0:06:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw Hatter. {Straw Hat-ya}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.03,0:06:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.24,0:06:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,...the guy we met at the Human Shop in Sabaody.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.64,0:06:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,His name is Trafalgar Law.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.80,0:06:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He is now...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.68,0:06:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, he's Traf... Tra-guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.88,0:06:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's his name!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.09,0:06:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He helped me get away from the battlefield
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.84,0:06:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and treated my wounds!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.76,0:06:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Your wounds?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.68,0:06:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.89,0:06:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Like Jinbe, he saved my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.64,0:06:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.91,0:06:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't expect to see you here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.84,0:07:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much for helping me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.00,0:07:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.86,0:07:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are the talking bear and the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.37,0:07:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Put Straw Hatter on my ship! {Straw Hat-ya}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.55,0:07:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna help him get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.15,0:07:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me take care of him for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.82,0:07:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.25,0:07:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Ace?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.19,0:07:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What is going to happen if we leave him like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.19,0:07:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.76,0:07:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I said when we got here,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.30,0:07:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,if his wound opens up, he will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.86,0:07:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw Hatter must take a complete rest for two more weeks. {Straw Hat-ya}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.39,0:07:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.64,0:07:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So you made it, Straw Hatter. {Straw Hat-ya}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.99,0:07:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But you don't have to thank me for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.49,0:07:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I just did it on the spur of the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.91,0:07:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We are both pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.46,0:08:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.79,0:08:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.79,0:08:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all enemies when it comes to the fight for the One Piece
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.38,0:08:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,but I owe so many people for helping me two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.94,0:08:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I just saw Jinbe and now you - I'm so lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.80,0:08:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.35,0:08:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, there is a Navy soldier on the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.33,0:08:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.84,0:08:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.76,0:08:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, help me, Trafalgar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.02,0:08:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Smoker-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.47,0:08:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.23,0:08:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Smoker-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.60,0:08:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Smo-yan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.44,0:08:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The Navy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.37,0:08:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Is she...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.91,0:08:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, Luffy! The Navy's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.05,0:08:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.54,0:08:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain-chan, what happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.63,0:09:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You alright, Smo-yan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.74,0:09:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Smoker-san!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.49,0:09:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought so! It's Smokey and his clan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.01,0:09:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.22,0:09:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a hole in his chest!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.80,0:09:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Smoker-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.13,0:09:26.46,Italics,,0,0,0,,To become a member of the Warlords...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.46,0:09:29.00,Italics,,0,0,0,,...he delivered the hearts of one hundred pirates
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.00,0:09:30.71,Italics,,0,0,0,,to the headquarters!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.71,0:09:32.29,Italics,,0,0,0,,He's crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.79,0:09:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.00,0:09:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.10,0:09:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.83,0:09:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.64,0:09:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa whoa, don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.58,0:09:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like these lame tearjerking scenes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.83,0:10:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.31,0:10:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Tashigi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.05,0:10:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Shambles!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.68,0:10:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! He took her down again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.60,0:10:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Smo-san's on the ground, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.61,0:10:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What did he just do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.74,0:10:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,She never learns.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.87,0:10:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get so serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.39,0:10:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Tashigi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.39,0:10:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy! Let's go! It's dangerous here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.95,0:10:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.37,0:10:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.42,0:10:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Tra-guy, I wanna ask you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.14,0:10:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Go round to the back of the laboratory.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.15,0:10:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What you're looking for is there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.95,0:10:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll see each other again later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.94,0:11:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We both have something we want to take back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.24,0:11:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. He was talking about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.00,0:11:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't be here. I'm a former pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.42,0:11:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, Luffy, let's get away from the Navy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.17,0:11:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Smokey and his clan will be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.73,0:11:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Did they lose to Tra-guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.67,0:11:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Straw Hat Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.24,0:11:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.44,0:11:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! This is no time for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.86,0:11:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Smo-san and Captain-chan are injured!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.52,0:11:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's freezing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.86,0:11:55.99,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,What should we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.86,0:11:58.13,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,1)}A MOUNTAIN BEHIND THE LABORATORY SANJI'S GROUP
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.99,0:11:58.13,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,The kids can't take it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.13,0:12:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's remove this fur and...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.71,0:12:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,No! It's my body!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.67,0:12:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't think we can find any warm coats around here...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.30,0:12:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't there a lodge or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.48,0:12:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,On top of that,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.48,0:12:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I need a camera and a mirror - and a sh-shower would be nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.88,0:12:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up or I'll tie you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.99,0:12:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's who?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.84,0:12:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The robot is scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.05,0:12:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Since it's come to this, you people,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.60,0:12:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I need you to put a leaf on your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.49,0:12:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.67,0:12:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The kids are collapsing from cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.09,0:12:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And I don't see any plants on this island!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.66,0:12:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So there are no leaves!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.95,0:12:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Then a stone or whatever is fine! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.28,0:12:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If you insist.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.37,0:12:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you have a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.66,0:12:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get them for the kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.48,0:12:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We got it. Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.59,0:13:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's a spell-to-make-it-not-cold kind of bullshit, I'll kick your ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.00,0:13:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.01,0:13:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Poof!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.82,0:13:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.52,0:13:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.91,0:13:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I got a coat and boots!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.80,0:13:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?! How did you do it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.43,0:13:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Gloves!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.63,0:13:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's warm!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.32,0:13:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Very warm!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.37,0:13:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing is I ate an unusual fruit one day
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.70,0:13:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and since then, I can use magic which allows me to disguise myself
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.41,0:13:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,or everyone else in any way I please.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.84,0:13:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know much about foreign clothes but will these suffice?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.80,0:13:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to warn you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.23,0:13:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Since it's magic, if you take those clothes off, they'll disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.95,0:14:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Cool! Head man! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.09,0:14:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He shouldn't have done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.40,0:14:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So he's a Devil Fruit user?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.07,0:14:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Devil?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.13,0:14:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But, wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.14,0:14:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If you had such power,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.47,0:14:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,why didn't you do it sooner?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.28,0:14:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It was nice to see her in a breast-band.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.45,0:14:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't wanna cover it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.61,0:14:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.22,0:14:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It itches! Itchy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.87,0:14:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll never say "ouch" or "I'm cold," will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.29,0:14:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a warrior!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.30,0:14:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are! Guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.73,0:14:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.51,0:15:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.31,0:15:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are they here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.56,0:15:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.07,0:15:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.14,0:15:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy and the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.30,0:15:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Zoro! Usopp! Robin! Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.31,0:15:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad to see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.65,0:15:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is that jackass cook jumping around?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.24,0:15:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He went nuts from cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.21,0:15:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? They look like giant children to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.40,0:15:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Shh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.22,0:15:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Hey, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.33,0:15:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do it, Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.64,0:15:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.73,0:16:06.40,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}THE STRAW HATS' ENCAMPMENT
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.77,0:16:03.98,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,We're here! This is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.98,0:16:07.36,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,This building has a similar style as the other one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.36,0:16:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's crumbling.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.82,0:16:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like there was a huge explosion or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.20,0:16:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine as long as it'll shelter us from the blizzard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.92,0:16:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, where should we begin?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.93,0:16:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I hurt my own delicate body!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.50,0:16:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll treat it right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.32,0:16:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Sanji-kun! What are you doing to my body?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.49,0:16:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Chopper.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.25,0:16:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I got my legs back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.92,0:16:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Leg-maro! Oh my hind legs!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.97,0:16:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you there is no creature like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.14,0:16:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,How surreal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.50,0:17:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He's quite original.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.20,0:17:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-The skeleton...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.78,0:17:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,...Just talked!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.23,0:17:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Nami-Sanji?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.05,0:17:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It was weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.43,0:17:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a dream of crossing a river.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.73,0:17:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a river running through giant boobs...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.65,0:17:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not the time for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.02,0:17:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, do the tank thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.91,0:17:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Show us the laser beam!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.63,0:17:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.15,0:17:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was it in his body?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.24,0:17:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.00,0:17:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to smoke, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.88,0:17:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's talk like adults, everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.72,0:17:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright. Now, who is who?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.82,0:18:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.44,0:18:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't come to me when you get wounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.45,0:18:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Chopper.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.82,0:18:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll treat your wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.03,0:18:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Nami.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.57,0:18:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I will never shoot the laser beam!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.25,0:18:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is our...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.75,0:18:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,...Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.92,0:18:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.68,0:18:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Was I always that indecent?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.89,0:18:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't do it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.56,0:18:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't hurt Nami-san anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.36,0:18:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't, Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.53,0:18:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami's gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.29,0:18:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If you touch my body, I'll make you pay 200,000 berries.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.91,0:18:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Peeping will be 100,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.24,0:18:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so cruel!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.71,0:18:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop laughing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.28,0:18:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't be so funny if it happened to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.20,0:18:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get it straight from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.66,0:18:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He is the samurai from the Wano Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.03,0:18:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The signal that we received was...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.24,0:19:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,...meant for the Alliga-taur
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.79,0:19:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,who they call "Boss" from one of his men.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.54,0:19:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It all started when this samurai sliced up all those centaurs.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.13,0:19:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But I just wanted to rescue my missing son - Momonosuke and cut those people
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.48,0:19:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,because they were standing in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.81,0:19:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.74,0:19:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That many children were held captive in the facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.33,0:19:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Momonosuke is still there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.55,0:19:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh, there were more children.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.30,0:19:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't even know the newcomers that well yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.73,0:19:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But the question is what happened after the signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.60,0:19:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's that man we just saw!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.59,0:19:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,People were saying that he is a Warlord.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.19,0:19:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.72,0:19:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean Tra-guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.93,0:19:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he become a Warlord?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.64,0:19:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, he joined them within past two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.28,0:20:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,He chopped me up into three pieces before I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.40,0:20:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,My head was kept in the facility!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.36,0:20:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,My torso was left there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.77,0:20:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And my legs were chased by a beast.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.48,0:20:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,When my legs were trying to get away using their wits,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.02,0:20:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,they stuck onto something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.56,0:20:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And that was the back of the dragon's head!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.57,0:20:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, you were cursing about a Warlord!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.17,0:20:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What? There were just legs, weren't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.55,0:20:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,How did he speak?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.18,0:20:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.39,0:20:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that was...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.51,0:20:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,...my farts.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.23,0:20:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It has always been my specialty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.92,0:20:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So you were fart-talking?! Yuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.57,0:20:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I was!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.52,0:20:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it smells when we're in a room.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.61,0:20:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,How funny to see a person with just a head and legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.38,0:20:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,By contrast, I just saw someone with just a torso.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.84,0:21:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That was his torso, obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.42,0:21:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.51,0:21:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.07,0:21:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Where?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.20,0:21:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you see my torso?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.15,0:21:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Are you... Tashigi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.66,0:21:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.33,0:21:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! So you're really Tashigi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.54,0:21:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,They got switched?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.58,0:21:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?! How did this happen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.54,0:21:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, are you okay without a heart, Tashigi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.21,0:21:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, strangely.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.91,0:21:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to talk to Captain-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.41,0:21:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.51,0:21:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,This one is so scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.93,0:21:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Smo-yan with Tashigi-chan's body!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.70,0:21:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It says "CC" on a ship hidden beside the laboratory.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.37,0:22:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What? There was such a ship, Vice Admiral Smoker?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.51,0:22:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. If it's left over from old days,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.23,0:22:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,the mark should be "PH"...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.53,0:22:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,...standing for Punk Hazard.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.67,0:22:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If there is some mastermind behind Law
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.84,0:22:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and if "CC" are his initials,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.30,0:22:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I know who it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.97,0:22:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If he's here on this island,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.73,0:22:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,it makes a lot of senses!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.40,0:22:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He is the former colleague of Dr.Vegapunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.05,0:22:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He is a scientist
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.60,0:22:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,named Caesar Clown!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.11,0:22:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell have you done, Law?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.88,0:23:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who should be complaining here!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.59,0:23:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Caesar!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.32,0:23:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,In the tumultuous New World, the ruler of Punk Hazard...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.84,0:23:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,...turns out to be an unexpectedly well-respected figure.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.47,0:23:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,As the Straw Hats recoil from this shocking fact...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.36,0:23:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,...Smoker tries to discover the true identity of this mysterious master.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.66,0:23:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.92,0:23:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,"The Worst in the World! A Scientist of Terror - Caesar!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.38,0:23:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
